summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 226W, page 15, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Green's Rich Acres, unrecorded, South 89 ft. of tracts 8 & 14, all of tracts 9 & 15, located approximately 630 ft. north of 110th between 3rd Ave. N.E. and 5th Ave. N.E. as Multiple Residence (RM) Zone.
